description:
Between you and Nikki, she knows Andrew is a best friend because they can share shoes. Andrew slept alone in the apartment last night as Nikki headed out to LA and sat next to a familiar friend, Joe Buck! You Heard it Here First, Nikki knows about a David Spade DM, Celeb gossip IG Deux Mois, the return of The Celebrity Dating Game and Nikki's mom joins in to hear Andrew's Weekly Sports Moment. They go through Listener Mail and in the Final Thought they talk about stand up vs. story telling.
